item.title: [+650] EXCLUSIVE: The Day Einstein Died (PICS)
item.description: Albert Einstein was 76 when he died. His funeral and cremation were intensely private affairs, and only one photographer managed to capture the events of that extraordinary day: LIFE magazine's Ralph Morse. But aside from one now-famous image (thumbnail), the pictures Morse took that day were never published until now.
